    "name": "SorobanLoyalty API",
    "description": "Complete API collection for the SorobanLoyalty platform.\n\n## Authentication\nThis API has no token-based authentication on read endpoints. Claim and redeem operations are submitted directly to the Soroban RPC from the frontend (signed by Freighter wallet) — they are not exposed as REST endpoints.\n\n## Environments\nSelect one of the bundled environments before running requests:\n- **local** — `http://localhost:3001`\n- **testnet** — your deployed testnet backend URL\n- **mainnet** — your deployed mainnet backend URL\n\n## Stellar Address\nSet `stellar_address` in the active environment to a valid 56-character Stellar public key (G…) to test the rewards endpoint.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
